 thanks to God. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 14:19","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":19},{"label":"1Co 10:30","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":30},{"label":"1Tm 4:3","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add but whoever does not observe the day, it is to the Lord that he does not observe it"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:14:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For none of us lives for himself, and no one dies for himself. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:38","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":38,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 5:15","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 2:20","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:20","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:38","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":38},{"label":"2Co 5:15","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":15},{"label":"Gl 2:20","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":20},{"label":"Php 1:20","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:14:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If we live, we live for the Lord; and if we die, we die for the Lord. Therefore, whether we live or die, we belong to the Lord. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 20:38","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":38,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:20","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 5:10","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 14:13","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":13,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 20:38","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":38},{"label":"Php 1:20","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":20},{"label":"1Th 5:10","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":10},{"label":"Rv 14:13","book":"Rev","chapter":14,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:14